org.sbolstandard.core

Interface DnaComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SBOLNamedObject, SBOLObject, SBOLRootObject, SBOLVisitable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DnaComponentImpl
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface DnaComponent
extends SBOLNamedObject, SBOLRootObject
    The SBOL data model's DnaComponent. This objects of this type represent DNA components for biological engineering which can be described by SequenceAnnotation objects and must specify their DnaSequence object. DnaComponents are expected to be found inside a SBOL Collection object.

      • setDescription

        void setDescription(String description)
        Deprecated. 
        Text which is written for users to read and interpret. It should describe what the component is used for and/or what it does. Suggestion: it should provide information that cannot yet be represented in the rest of the DNA components computable fields. Do not include tags such as HTML or XML inside as that may break the RDF. Don't include {} tags as that may break the Json.
        Specified by:
        setDescription in interface SBOLNamedObject
        Parameters:
        description - human readable text describing the component
